INSERT INTO `products` VALUES ('2','30','8','Bahubali Laser Land Leveller','bahubali-laser-land-leveller','Apogee’s Bahubali Zero Slope Laser Levelling Kit offers a complete precision farming solution. This integrated setup includes a robust Bahubali land leveller, high-accuracy laser receiver, rugged control panel, bucket scrapper, and long-range laser transmitter. Engineered for large-scale Indian farms, it ensures uniform land levelling, water savings, and increased yield.','<ul>
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES ('3','30','7','Dual-Slope-Bahubali-Laser-Land-Leveller','dual-slope-bahubali-laser-land-leveller','Dual Slope Bahubali Laser Land Levelling Kit from Apogee Agrotech is a robust and intelligent solution for precision land grading. It features the powerful Bahubali Dual Slope Leveller for accurate slope setting, a durable laser transmitter & receiver combo, a smart control panel, and a high-efficiency bucket scrapper – all designed for large-scale Indian farms. This advanced system helps improve crop productivity, reduce irrigation costs, and level land with dual-axis accuracy.','<ul>
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES ('7','30','8','Fighter Laser Land Leveller','fighter-laser-land-leveller','Fighter Zero Slope Laser Land Levelling Kit by Apogee Agrotech is engineered for robust and accurate field operations. Designed for heavy-duty tractors and tough terrains, the kit includes the Fighter series leveller with zero slope control, precision laser transmitter, durable receiver, user-friendly control panel, and a strong bucket scrapper. This kit helps farmers save water, increase crop yields, and achieve consistent land levels with every use.','<ul>
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES ('9','29','6','2D GNSS Land Leveller','2d-gnss-land-leveller','2D GNSS Land Leveller by Apogee Agrotech India is an advanced GPS Land Leveler designed for high-precision land preparation. As a leading GNSS Leveling Machine, it supports efficient water usage and optimized crop growth. Trusted as a top-tier Smart Agriculture Equipment, it is one of the most reliable Precision Farming Tools in India, empowering farmers with accuracy, speed, and modern farming technology.','<ul>
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES ('10','30','8','Standard Laser Land Leveller','standard-laser-land-leveller','Apogee Standard Zero Slope Laser Land Levelling Kit delivers reliable and consistent levelling performance for medium to large Indian farms. This set includes a Standard Zero Slope Leveller, precision Laser Receiver, rugged Control Panel, wide-range Laser Transmitter, and efficient Bucket Scrapper – perfect for reducing water usage and increasing crop uniformity.','<ul>
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES ('12','30','7','Dual Slope Fighter Laser Land Leveller','dual-slope-fighter-laser-land-leveller','Apogee Dual Slope Fighter Laser Levelling Kit is a heavy-duty, high-precision agricultural solution. It combines Apogee’s powerful Fighter Land Leveller with intelligent dual slope laser guidance, a smart control panel, rugged scrapper, and reliable receiver/transmitter setup—perfect for complex field gradients and maximum water-saving land preparation.','<ul>
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES ('13','30','7','Dual Slope Standard Laser Land Leveller','dual-slope-standard-laser-land-leveller','Apogee Dual Slope Standard Laser Land Levelling Kit is designed to deliver accurate land grading with smart slope management. This professional-grade solution includes the Standard Dual Slope Leveller, high-precision Laser Receiver, programmable Control Panel, powerful Laser Transmitter, and rugged Bucket Scrapper – everything required for modern precision farming.','<ul>
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES ('14','28','4','Super Rotavator','super-rotavator','Apogee Super Rotavator is your answer to challenging soil conditions. Built for hard, dry, and compact soil types, it performs deep tillage with unmatched strength and efficiency. Ideal for sugarcane, cotton, wheat, and paddy fields, this rotavator ensures a uniform seedbed in fewer passes.','<ul>
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES ('15','28','3','Super Max Rotavator','super-max-rotavator','Apogee Super Max Rotavator is a heavy-duty rotavator designed for deep tillage and maximum soil pulverization. As a leading tractor rotavator in India, it’s the ideal max depth farming tool for tough field conditions. Choose the trusted power of Apogee Rotavator for unmatched performance.','<ul>
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES ('16','30','15','RL-700 Transmitter','rl-700-transmitter','The Laser Equipment Kit is a complete solution designed to deliver high-precision land leveling for modern agriculture. Engineered with advanced laser technology, the kit ensures uniform field surfaces, improved water management, and enhanced crop yields.','<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">The <strong>Laser Equipment Kit</strong> is a complete solution designed to deliver <strong>high-precision land leveling</strong> for modern agriculture. Engineered with advanced laser technology, the kit ensures uniform field surfaces, improved water management, and enhanced crop yields.</span></span></p>
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES ('17','30','15','LD Receiver','ld-receiver','Laser Receiver is mounted on the leveling bucket or scraper and detects the laser 
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES ('18','30','15','RL-600 Transmitter','rl-600-transmitter','Laser Transmitter emits a stable, 360° rotating laser beam that defines a perfectly level 
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES ('19','30','15','Control Box 200','control-box-200','It detects the height of the laser beam and sends signals to the control box to adjust the hydraulic valve — ensuring the bucket maintains the correct cutting or filling position.','<ul>
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES ('20','30','15','HD Receiver','hd-receiver','Laser Receiver is mounted on the leveling bucket or scraper and detects the laser beam emitted by the transmitter. It detects the height of the laser beam and sends signals to the control box to adjust the hydraulic valve — ensuring the bucket maintains the correct cutting or filling position.','<ul>
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES ('21','30','15','RL-800 Transmitter','rl-800-transmitter','Laser Transmitter emits a stable, 360° rotating laser beam that defines a perfectly level reference plane over the entire working area.','<ul>
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES ('22','29','5','3D GNSS LAND LEVELLER','3d-gnss-land-leveller','3D GNSS Land Leveller by Apogee Agrotech India is an advanced GPS Land Leveler designed for high-precision land preparation. As a leading GNSS Leveling Machine, it supports efficient water usage and optimized crop growth. Trusted as a top-tier Smart Agriculture Equipment, it is one of the most reliable Precision Farming Tools in India, empowering farmers with accuracy, speed, and modern farming technology.','<ul>
