<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">This equipment kit consists of Laser Receiver, Laser Transmitter &amp; Laser Control Panel, working together to achieve unmatched leveling accuracy and operational efficiency.</span></span></p>

<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><strong>Laser Transmitter </strong>emits a stable, 360&deg; rotating laser beam that defines a perfectly level reference plane over the entire working area.</span></span></p>

<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><strong>Laser Receiver </strong>is mounted on the leveling bucket or scraper and detects the laser beam emitted by the transmitter. It detects the height of the laser beam and sends signals to the control box to adjust the hydraulic valve &mdash; ensuring the bucket maintains the correct cutting or filling position.</span></span></p>

<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><strong>Laser Control Box</strong> processes signals from the receiver and automatically regulates the tractor&rsquo;s hydraulic system. It controls the movement of the leveling bucket by communicating with the hydraulic valve, ensuring precise leveling according to the reference plane.</span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Applications:</span></span></p>

<ul>
	<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Agricultural land leveling</span></span></li>
	<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Construction sites</span></span></li>
	<li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Field preparation for irrigation or drainage systems</span></span></li>
</ul>','<p>.</p>','[\"9601769146926_website img 10.jpg\",\"4741769152125_RL700.jpg\"]',NULL,'1','2025-10-27 19:26:43','2026-01-23 07:08:45',NULL,'Laser Land Leveller Equipment Kit – Zero Level, Apogee Agrotech','Laser Land Leveller Equipment Kit – Zero Level, Apogee Agrotech','Laser Land Leveller Equipment Kit – Zero Level offers high-precision land leveling for modern agriculture with advanced laser technology by Apogee Agrotech.',NULL);
